Great show.  My kids(boys) and I love Queen Latifah.  She is a great actress!!  Sure the movie is predictable, but aren't they all pretty much.  This is just a great movie to sit down and have a laugh.  Buy it!  Houseguest on the other hand, was ok....maybe 3 stars.  But Bringing Down The House is funny.
Two of the funniest movies ever... won't be a waste of money here if you love comedies.  Add Major Payne and it would have been PERFECT.
This movie is hilarious.  Queen Latifah and Steve Martin can make any movie.  I enjoyed this movie and would recommend it to anyone.
